td.div: Deutsch: Die „Saint Patrick's Flag“, die dritte Komponente des Union Jack. Sie repräsentiert Irland.

English: This is "Saint Patrick's saltire", the third component of the Union Flag. It represents Ireland and is called "Saint Patrick's cross/saltire", though whether this was originally an authentic symbol of Saint Patrick is historically quite doubtful.
Español: Bandera de San Patricio: unas líneas rojas en un campo de blanco
